<p id="mwiA">representing two component waveforms <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt276" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"F"}}' id="mwiQ"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle F}">
