</span></dd></dl>

<p id="mwAmQ">the Fourier transform is:</p>

<dl id="mwAmU"><dd id="mwAmY"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt364" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\tilde{ f} (k) = \\sigma e^{-\\sigma^2 k^2 / 2} \\ . "}}' id="mwAmc"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\tilde {f}}(k)=\sigma e^{-\sigma ^{2}k^{2}/2}\ .}">
  <semantics>
